{"word":"G1340 - διϊσχυρίζομαι - diïschyrízomai - dee-is-khoo-rid'-zom-ahee - Confidently affirm","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διϊσχυρίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>diïschyrízomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>dee-is-khoo-rid'-zom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Confidently affirm"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சாதி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to lean upon, to affirm stoutly, to assert confidently"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2478 - ἰσχυρός - ischyrós - is-khoo-ros'/2478\">G2478</a>; to <i>stout</i> it <i>through</i>, that is, <i>asseverate:</i> - confidently (constantly) affirm."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}